\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs20 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7408022\charrsid11479981 {\*\bkmkstart Memo2}
Self-evaluation can affect cognitive performance (e.g. memory, reasoning, learning etc.). This project aims to try and understand the mechanisms by which self-assessment changes cognitive performance. The project will identi
fy how different people respond to self-evaluation and how self-evaluation can most effectively be designed (e.g. worded, timed etc.)
\par {\*\bkmkend Memo2}
