\par 79 - Is your proposed research a clinical trial? A clinic
al trial is a form of research designed to find out the effects of an intervention, including a treatment or diagnostic procedure. A clinical trial can involve testing a drug, a surgical procedure, other therapeutic procedures and devices, a preventive pr
ocedure, or a diagnostic device or procedure.
